 individuals manage and resolve legal disputes of all sizes. Whether you’re bringing a claim or defending court proceedings, we’ll guide you through the process with straightforward, practical advice. Court isn’t always the answer. Wherever possible, we look for efficient ways to resolve disputes through alternative dispute resolution, to save time, reduce costs, and preserve important relationships.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"service-type_header_content-background\"><div class=\"circle is-header\"></div></div></div><div class=\"service-type_breadcrumb-component\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large full-bleed-18\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall full-bleed-20\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component full-bleed-21\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"aligned-right\" class=\"breadcrumb_component w-variant-5112baff-e12b-04f8-68dc-4d6a7dc9da49\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/for-individuals\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">For individuals</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Dispute Resolution</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_service-link\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"service-link_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid service-link_content\"><div class=\"service-link_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Services</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Your interests come first. We work with you to agree a clear strategy from the outset, focused on protecting your position and achieving the right outcome. You’ll always know where you stand and what the next step looks like.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"mailto:CDREnquiry@moonstone.co.ug\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Speak to an expert</p></div></a></div></div></div><div class=\"service-link_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"service-link_list w-dyn-items\"><div data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" element-reveal=\"target\" data-scroll=\"\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"service-link_list-item w-dyn-item\"><div arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" class=\"service-link_item-div\"><a href=\"/dispute-resolution/banking-financial-disputes\" class=\"service-link_item w-inline-block\"><div class=\"service-link_item-text-wrapper\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xxsmall\"><p class=\"text-size-large\">Banking &amp; Finance Disputes</p></div><div class=\"margin-bottom\"><p>We help individuals challenge insurers, brokers and advisers to recover losses and secure the compensation they deserve.</p></div></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-secondary\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.5