slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Thank you to Danielle for all her effort during this process, obviously not one I wanted to be in, but Danielle has made it a much clearer and less stressful one.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Just wanted to say that Danielle&#x27;s helpfulness, generosity of time, and straightforward way of discussing things so far have already been really refreshing regarding this awkward process. It is really appreciated.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Paula was brilliant throughout, providing help, support and advice during an incredibly long and drawn-out situation that should never have reached that point in the first place. I’m truly grateful for everything she did.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Moonstone Advocates. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">There are two stand-out individuals I feel it is necessary to mention. I have had the pleasure of working with both Andrew Morgan and Darren Morgan as part of the legal team on a recent trial. It has been clear throughout my time working with them that the client feels entirely at ease with each of them – they are trusted and have a way of ensuring the clie</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Luke Patel is highly experienced in a range of disputes, often property-related. Darren Morgan brings a very calm air to matters, such that clients have great confidence in his unruffled manner. Yat Wong is particularly experienced in professional negligence matters. Aimee Hutchinson has a wide range of experience including in judicial review matters arising</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals, across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Luke Patel is stand out. Very ‘savvy’. Sound judgment. On top of the issues. Deploys commercial outlook. Excellent client dealing skills.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section_crosslink\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"crosslink_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid crosslink_content\"><div class=\"crosslink_content-left\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Other related services</h2></div><div class=\"w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"crosslink_item-list w-dyn-items\"><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"crosslink_item w-dyn-item\"><a list-link=\"trigger\" href=\"/leasehold-enfranchisement-management\" class=\"button is-text-link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"crosslink_item-text-wrapper\"><p>Leasehold Enfranchisement &amp; Management</p></div><div list-link=\"target\" class=\"crosslink_item-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M676.2-445.93H188.09q-14.68 0-24.37-9.7-9.7-9.7-9.7-24.37 0-14.67 9.7-24.37 9.69-9.7 24.37-9.7H676.2L456.13-734.13q-10.2-10.2-10.33-24.03-.14-13.84 10.07-24.09 10.22-10.29 24.09-10.17 13.87.12 24.15 10.31l278 278q5.46 5.52 7.94 11.48 2.49 5.97 2.49 12.66t-2.49 12.63q-2.48 5.95-7.94 11.45l-278.24 278q-10.55 10.43-24.17 10.43-13.61 0-23.81-10.49-10.19-10.21-10.19-23.85 0-13.63 10.19-23.83l220.31-220.3Z\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"crosslink_item w-dyn-item\"><a list-link=\"trigger\" href=\"/landlord-financing-conveyancing\" class=\"button is-text-link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"crosslink_item-text-wrapper\"><p>Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing</p></div><div list-link=\"target\" class=\"crosslink_item-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M676.2-445.93H188.09q-